  ('“Be yourself; everyone else is already taken.”', 'Oscar Wilde', 'Motivation'),
  ('“You''ve gotta dance like there''s nobody watching,Love like you''ll never be hurt,Sing like there''s nobody listening,And live like it''s heaven on earth.”', 'William W. Purkey', 'Motivation'),
